Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, this film, along with the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,others beautifully depicts the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,impact accessible tech has on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,people's lives when you design
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for everyone, including people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with a range of disabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here today to ask you to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,join the campaign with us in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,designing your apps and games to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,work for everyone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we inherently design for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ourselves, because we design to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what we know, our own world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have wants and needs, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,passions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We think of features, make an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,app, join a company to put those
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ideas out there for others too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless, the next step of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching more people is putting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself in their shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to figure out who we
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,might be excluding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought about how there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,might be other people out in the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,world with the same passions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,needs and wants as you, but
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,can't use your app?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we think about how there are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,more than one billion active
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple devices out there, which
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is a lot of potential customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and knowing that one in seven
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,people in the world have a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,disability, we can be sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,people who may want to use our
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and platforms will lie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere across a spectrum of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,abilities and capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Human abilities vary greatly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,across cognition and social
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,abilities; dexterity, mobility,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,vision and hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And in order to understand and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,comprehend information, our
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,perception through sight, sound
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and touch are essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if you inhibit one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of those senses, or take one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That could happen to you or I in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,our lifetime, gradually or
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People with physical
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,disabilities will include
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,extreme cases, like cerebral
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,palsy and paralysis, but also
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,include conditions like carpal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,tunnel syndrome, or temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions such as a broken
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People with vision loss will
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,include blindness, low vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and colorblindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But also, situational
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,disabilities like screen glare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and temporary day blindness that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we all experience when emerging
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from a dark movie theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing loss is one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,leading types of hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,disabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's from birth or it's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,prevalent with age, made for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,iPhone hearing aids are changing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,people's quality of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we extend our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,notification queues to having
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all visual, oral, and tactile
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,feedback, we're enabling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone to get their
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you may have heard the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,statistic that 1 in 68 children
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States have been
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,identified with the autism
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,spectrum disorder, according to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the CDC.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Autistic individuals can be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,sensitive to unexpected sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and distracting graphics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are also many adults
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and children with dyslexia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Having multiple visual and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,auditory options help people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with dyslexia and is also widely
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,used by the blind and people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with low vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if we think about how
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone in the world will have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a range of abilities and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,capabilities, the next step of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching more people is making
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,your apps accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the word accessible wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,invented to describe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,accommodating those with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,disabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about access, whoever we
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Easily reached or obtained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Easily used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Easily understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone. Whether you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,permanent or situational
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,impairment, young or old, new or
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,pro to technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever language you sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,speak, or read would love access
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to great apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we can design better
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,apps for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To help you do this, we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk about some design
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,considerations and workflow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,techniques to keep in mind when
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,making your apps work for more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By being inclusive, not only can
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we help everyone function in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,their daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can also create new
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,possibilities throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, today, we're going to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,about three areas of designing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Striving for simplicity, making
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,our apps effortless and easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Accessing perceivability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Making sure our apps are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,understandable through sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sound, and haptics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And designing with integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding ourselves accountable
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for ethically making sure we
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,include everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are principles applied to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,making great experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, first if we think about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is simple to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we think of it being effortless
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,without difficulties, hurdles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or cognitive strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But for something to feel simple
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that does mean it can't do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,complex things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means trying to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,desired outcomes in the most
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,effortless and elegant way
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that aren't simple create
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,barriers of entry to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As we go through our day, the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,requirements of work and life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly drains our energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we are low on energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we have less energy to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,troubleshoot tech and less
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,patience for navigating
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,something that should be quick
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At night, we rest and recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, were you aware that one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in six children in the United
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,States have a developmental
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,disability?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It ranges from mild
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,disabilities, such as speech and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,language impairments to serious
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,developmental disabilities, such
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as intellectual disabilities and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,autism.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For people who have cognitive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,disabilities and/or chronic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,illnesses, they might start out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the day at three-quarters of a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And tasks take extra effort
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, if you exert yourself all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to empty on one day, you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,might start out the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the apps that we make do a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,great job at helping us through
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,our day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a convenience or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,helping us to recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They provide quick and easy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,access to services, which is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely important for those
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,who may have difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,traveling outside of the home,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking a hearing on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,or juggling work and home life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, convenience apps
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,like Instacart, you can have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,groceries delivered to your door
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,which alleviates the stress of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the supermarket, or allows you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to rest at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it just gives you time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,back with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With education apps like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doulingo it's incredible that we
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,can learn from the comforts of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,our home, on our own time, at
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our own speed, and with health
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,apps like Calm, they help us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,nurture our mental and physical
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And with content creation apps
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,like iMovie, we can create and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,share our artistry with friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,family and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, apps play a key role in our
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,daily lives now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can make even more impact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in people's lives by reducing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the amount of effort that we
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,require to use our apps, which
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,reduces barriers and provides
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,more access.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is easier said than
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So here are some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should strive for our apps to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,be easy to navigate by having
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,them similarly structured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be able to get
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,started and complete common task
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,without encountering any
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,barriers or issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And we should use UIKit as much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as possible to achieve the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,consistent behaviors within each
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,app and across apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because UIKit wasn't made for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just developers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a design language for the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,platform that everyone is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar with and knows how to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are design resources
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,on human interface guidelines to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,help you use the standard UIKit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,components in your apps during
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the design phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,these toolkits support many
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility accommodations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we can consistently use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,standard UIKit interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,patterns and components for more
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,task of our apps like basic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,structure and navigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sign-up flows, account settings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and sharing then you can spend
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the majority of your time on the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,parts of your apps that make
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,them special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And making sure those parts are
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,accessible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Consistent use of our design
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,language is beneficial because
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you learn one app you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,serious head start on learning
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,another because repetition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,creates cognitive ease and a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,comforting feeling of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we know it's not always
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,possible, to solely use UIKit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when you need to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,do something unique and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,original, but don't forget about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you think more
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,holistically about the products
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're putting out into the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Building on what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Making use of standard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,components and familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,interaction patterns to help
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,make apps easy to navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Be laser focused in your
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Reduce any hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me get started quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just works like I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,expected it to consistently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our products need to be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,understandable and perceivable
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that information
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,needs to be available to at
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,least one sense; sight, sound or
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,touch that is available to each
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can look at our apps and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,ask ourselves is it legible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it audible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it tactile?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But before we look at
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,legibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's escape for a moment to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this beautiful beach and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,experience it in a few different
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, watch the waves roll in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Soak up that sunshine for a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have vision loss, you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,might not get to see this in all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of its glory, but you're hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,would be more sensitive to these
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Ocean Sounds ]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or if you're colorblind, you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,might see the world more like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or if you're blind, you're
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,likely even more in-tune to the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And these situations are very
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world, 285 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,are estimated to have moderate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or severe vision loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And 39 million of those are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,completely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And one in 12 men are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,colorblind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And best estimates are around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,360 million people in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,have disabling hearing loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only can hearing and vision
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,loss limit people from
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,distinguishing information, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they will also be seeing and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,hearing your brand in different
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,ways than you expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, someone with low
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,vision may see their phones like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you aren't low vision
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself, you can simulate low
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,vision by using a small blur in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,your design software.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, people with low vision will
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,often learn the location of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,icons as long as they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But content areas are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they need to maintain high
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,visual contrast to increase
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,legibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you get started, you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,should ask yourself is your app
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,legible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because maximizing legibility is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest benefit on being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,able to comprehend information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's less work on us to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,interpret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, when we have key
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,information that is low in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,contrasts because of small fonts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and low color contrast ratios,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or thin fonts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be painful to read and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you experience cognitive strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a good place to start to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,correct low contrast is to use
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the default textile body for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,your main content and a high
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,color contrast with your
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,background.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can use bolder font
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,weights to emphasize text or
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,titles, rather than thin fonts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can use filled in button
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,shapes so that the text contrast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is high, and the way forward in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,your app is really clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't use textiles or
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,system fonts in your app, it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,would be ideal to support the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility bold text
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,settings, which requires you to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,increase your font weights by
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,two weights thicker when the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,setting is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is built-in with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,system fonts and textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The new App Store design does an
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,excellent job at maximizing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,legibility through its bold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,typography, prominent buy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,buttons, large fonts, and high
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,color contrast colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On macOS, there are increased
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast settings as well, that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when on all active controls
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,become higher contrast by making
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,backgrounds opaque, button
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,outlines becomes thicker and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,darker and system colors become
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,darker to create high color
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast ratios.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So now that you know to look
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for, let's look at the before
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and after again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And even the ruled lines and the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,color values of gray text
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You will need to supply these
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,same alternate designs, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,do not use standard AppKit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because they will not come for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,free in custom UI, but they're
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely important for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,maximizing legibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the next suggestion to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,increase legibility maybe the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,most important thing to take
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,away today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's to support dynamic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,type, or the text size setting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because this feature increases
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,legibility by allowing each
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,person to personalize their
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,experience by increasing the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,font size.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe you need a farther
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,viewing distance if mounted on a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,chair or propped on a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when our fonts don't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,scale, people with low vision
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,need to use screen zoom windows
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to read the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like having to turn your
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,light on, or your magnifier in a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,dimly lit restaurant to read the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But except this is all day and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people don't bother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with zoom windows at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They painfully read the small
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,type or use their phones for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,short periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not a great
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you adopt dynamic type by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,using textiles and use the new
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,standard spacing constraints, we
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can offer a larger reading
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,experience without needing zoom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And new this year in iOS 11 is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic type support for custom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,fonts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, if you access
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,larger text setting via the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,general settings, there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,switch that enables even larger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility text sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And this year, in iOS 11, all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,textiles will support these
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,larger settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this means that we need to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,design responsive layouts to be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,able to handle these large font
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To do this for our own platform
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,apps this year, a team of us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,took a step back and developed a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,few simple principles that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,helped guide us through a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,system-wide audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The first principle was to make
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as much text dynamic as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and to support these
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility text sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is make good use of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,screen width by wrapping lines
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of type, rather than truncating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, displaying the same
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,amount of text at the larger
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,sizes as with the default UI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly, scaling glyphs that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,appear next to text in content
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,areas so that the glyphs scale
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,with the text in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we look at all of these
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,together in practice it really
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,gets magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The mail screen now grows the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,whole mail message to a zoom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,level of 315% from the default
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,size.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And in custom layouts, like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,calendar, this year we made even
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,more content scale like the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,month grid increase in size,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,where it didn't support dynamic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,type it all before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the larger accessibility
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,sizes, we re-laid out the event
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,row similar to the watch layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in the end, the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,character count per line was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it allowed maximum screen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,width for text.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now if we turn on the bold
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,text setting and simulate low
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,vision with the blur, and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,compare it next to the largest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,currently shipping screen on the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,left, now people with vision
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,loss will be able to use this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,app more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've designed these responsive
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,layouts in most native UIKit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, like action sheets,
