Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,space if we scaled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We added a larger representation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Fortis in a central hub
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can get via Long Press.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also added larger
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,popovers for segmented controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've also extended larger
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,tech support to system spaces
