Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there are a few we missed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this year, but we have plans for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,more and if you support iKit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you will get these updates for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,free as we make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, maximizing legibility and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,providing scalable dynamic type
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,improves visual experience for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And alongside text that is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and understandable, same applies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for media and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All dialogue should support
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,captions because captions
