Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which gives more access to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,people, whether you have hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,loss, in a public setting, or
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe even learning a new
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,language.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like trying to watch a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,video or a game intro with the
