Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or trying to read someone's lips
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that aren't looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like you only get about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,half the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, apps like Kitchen Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have added captions to all of
