Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,OK so along with sight is sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask yourself, are your
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,apps audible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's listen to a clip of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the intro design for Carlos V.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,video again and listen to the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,significance of the audible cues
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the app along with VoiceOver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that he's using to navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, VoiceOver is a built-in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,screen reader that speaks the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,content on screen for people who
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,may be blind or have low vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ReverbNation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Double tap to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Text field.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dictate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Album will be dropping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,worldwide on April 14, 2017!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow our ReverbNation page.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Done. Successfully shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, we can hear VoiceOver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:22:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,navigating the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The custom sounds of the apps
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,messaging feature, and dictation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to input the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Altogether, this creates an
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,experience that is accessible to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Carlos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, adding thoughtful sounds to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,app interactions helps you know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,where you are, what you've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it's just delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, checking out VoiceOver in a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,system is as easy as asking Siri
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn VoiceOver on and off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't know the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,VoiceOver's like I have a quick
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,demo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be swiping across the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,screen to advance the selection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,through some apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But then since I know that the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,phone app is in my dock, I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.59,0:23:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,going to tap the lower left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,corner of the screen and then
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,double tap to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> VoiceOver on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mail. No unread emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Calendar. Monday, June 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos. Camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dock. Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Phone. Add.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Edit button.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:23:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy Frost iPhone button.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, and there are tutorials
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and documentation on Apple's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,developer site to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,become even more familiar and to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to support this in your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, if you have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,image-based apps, we need to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,allow image descriptions to be
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,added at share time by the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,poster so that VoiceOver can
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,have something personalized to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,describe the photo with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, new in VoiceOver this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.41,0:24:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,year is image analysis to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.59,0:24:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,describe the image contents or
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,composition, or if type is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,overlaid on images.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But a handcrafted description
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.14,0:24:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,will always be preferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.02,0:24:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Twitter has done a great job at
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,adding image description options
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.41,0:24:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to their Tweet sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.68,0:24:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, another area that reduces
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.16,0:24:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hurdles and barriers for apps is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,integrating with Siri.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.05,0:24:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Siri is the ultimate quick
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.89,0:24:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,access to your app that doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.47,0:24:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,even require looking or holding,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or touching the screen, with
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.11,0:24:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,this voice activation and speech
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.79,0:25:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,input.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.79,0:25:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hands-free and eyes free.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can control my home, send
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,messages, and even start
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.53,0:25:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,workouts quickly with apps like
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.09,0:25:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zova.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.66,0:25:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, new this year is being
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.49,0:25:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,able to type to Siri that is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,available in accessibility
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.11,0:25:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This gives quick access to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.82,0:25:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who may not be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.81,0:25:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.39,0:25:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you're just in a public
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, lastly, along with sight and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.72,0:25:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,sound, is touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.72,0:25:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask yourself, are your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.03,0:25:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,apps tactile?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.86,0:25:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On supported devices adding
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.37,0:25:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,haptics provides a way to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.21,0:25:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,physically engage people through
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.46,0:25:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets your attention if sight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.04,0:25:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and sound are not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.72,0:25:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But also, provides an
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,enhancement for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.69,0:25:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, some
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.88,0:25:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,system-provided interface
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,elements such as switches,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.06,0:25:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sliders, pickers, index
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.04,0:25:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,scrubbers provide haptic
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.94,0:25:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,feedback when we interact with
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.17,0:25:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,them to reinforce the action
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.36,0:26:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.29,0:26:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And a haptic on pull to refresh,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.11,0:26:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let's you know that you've
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the critical threshold
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.63,0:26:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,between scrolling and refreshing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.87,0:26:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that shares a continuous
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.26,0:26:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.09,0:26:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And likewise, with swipe to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The haptic provides the critical
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.86,0:26:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,threshold of the accelerated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,delete swipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.55,0:26:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then another example is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.14,0:26:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Siri.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It uses a success haptic as a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,confirmation that she heard what
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.91,0:26:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.73,0:26:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Apple Pay uses visuals
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.89,0:26:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,haptics and sound with the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,confirmation for the successful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.76,0:26:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.85,0:26:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels the way it looks and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.41,0:26:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds, leaving me with a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.72,0:26:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,confident purchase or payment
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.16,0:26:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ding].
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.22,0:27:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.11,0:27:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to see if your apps are
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.71,0:27:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,perceivable, ask yourself is it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.24,0:27:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,legible?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.34,0:27:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.77,0:27:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it audible?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.70,0:27:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it usable without site?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.06,0:27:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it tactile?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.10,0:27:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.74,0:27:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one away, or even two of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.39,0:27:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,these can I still understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.37,0:27:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, now my colleague AJ is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.34,0:27:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,going to talk about what they
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.73,0:27:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,did in the Maps Team this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.57,0:27:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,applying some of these methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.52,0:27:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.00,0:27:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.58,0:27:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.04,0:27:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In Maps we collaborated closely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.86,0:27:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with Caroline and the platform
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.10,0:27:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,team.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this year we put into
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.17,0:27:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,practice a lot of what she's
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.72,0:27:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,covered today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.04,0:27:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, before we get into a few of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.40,0:27:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,those examples, and think about
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.81,0:27:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,how to design with integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.87,0:27:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to take a short
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.98,0:27:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.49,0:27:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to add a couple of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.36,0:28:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes to our ETA.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.34,0:28:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've used maps for thousands of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.83,0:28:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,years to plan, direct, to travel
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.41,0:28:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and to help us explore the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.97,0:28:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And maps of the past, like this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.50,0:28:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,one, beautiful as they remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.41,0:28:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,were not accessible at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.06,0:28:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't zoom on this map
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.82,0:28:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,without a magnifying glass, and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.92,0:28:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't orient yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.08,0:28:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,upon it without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.72,0:28:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In face the only manipulating
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.54,0:28:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you could do would be to fold
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.04,0:28:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.76,0:28:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as our understanding of the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.77,0:28:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,world has improved, so have our
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.83,0:28:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.44,0:28:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, your map understands
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.70,0:28:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.30,0:28:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It knows the direction you're
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.35,0:28:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.01,0:28:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It knows the device you're
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.92,0:28:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,using, and it's equipped with
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.08,0:28:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,your individual preferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.70,0:28:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's updated every day with new
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.68,0:28:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,information.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.73,0:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can search it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.84,0:29:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can mark it indestructibly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.93,0:29:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and make it your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.50,0:29:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It can take you places in real
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.17,0:29:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,time, avoiding traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.71,0:29:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hopefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.29,0:29:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And in iOS 11, you can even see
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.45,0:29:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,inside venues.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is, today our mediums
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.12,0:29:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are so versatile, they provide
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.32,0:29:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,us with the incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.25,0:29:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.90,0:29:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when I joined Maps, I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.34,0:29:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,remember thinking a lot about
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.61,0:29:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,how crazy it felt to see inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.00,0:29:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like looking through a keyhole
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and stepping through this icon,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.87,0:29:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot have imagined the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.53,0:29:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,operation I saw behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.55,0:29:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it almost completely for
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.12,0:29:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.06,0:29:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone who uses our apps
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.65,0:29:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,are the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.46,0:29:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't care how hard it was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.79,0:29:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.41,0:29:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not important that it works
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.79,0:29:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for Johnny Appleseed or Jane
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.85,0:29:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.47,0:29:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is that it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.77,0:29:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.89,0:30:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.25,0:30:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine going to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.80,0:30:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought your ticket and your
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.02,0:30:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,excited to watch the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.12,0:30:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The theater's packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.93,0:30:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to your seat and there's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.53,0:30:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a pillar in front of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.24,0:30:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,completely blocking your view.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.68,0:30:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I'm not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.99,0:30:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,come back to that cinema.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.53,0:30:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm no longer just a regular
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.89,0:30:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maps user, not that there's any
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.82,0:30:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.62,0:30:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to build a map of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.52,0:30:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire world and it's a big
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.03,0:30:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and diverse place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.54,0:30:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you, I'm on a team
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.29,0:30:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,responsible for everyone's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.06,0:30:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.27,0:30:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, coming back to simplicity
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.87,0:30:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and perceivability.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.22,0:30:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maps are not exact replicas of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.40,0:30:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,environments.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.14,0:30:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes photographic detail is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.18,0:30:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.52,0:30:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But most people don't find the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.40,0:30:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,satellite view practical in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.52,0:30:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We use simplified abstracted
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.06,0:31:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,representations, designed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.37,0:31:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,easy to understand and faster
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.19,0:31:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to process to help us
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.57,0:31:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,orient ourselves more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.53,0:31:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's why we provide a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.46,0:31:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,transit map too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.36,0:31:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where we suppress some elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.46,0:31:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,like places or minor roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.59,0:31:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which aren't as relevant to you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.10,0:31:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,once you're using transit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.16,0:31:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And we do all this for
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.26,0:31:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.44,0:31:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And we make sure our maps are
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.18,0:31:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Visually, audibly, and through
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.03,0:31:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,haptic feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We put a lot of care into
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.56,0:31:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping the navigation screen as
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.04,0:31:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,simple as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.50,0:31:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important information
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.78,0:31:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,available at a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.40,0:31:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can understand quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.12,0:31:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and stay focused on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.71,0:31:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you're walking or
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,taking transit, audible
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.14,0:31:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,directions spoken clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.08,0:31:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Starting route to San Jose
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.40,0:31:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,McEnery Convention Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.08,0:31:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Imagine if Siri mumbled these
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.98,0:31:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,instructions incomprehensibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.15,0:32:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because isn't that kind of the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.53,0:32:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,equivalent to small, blurry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.15,0:32:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,information.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.30,0:32:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And on your wrist, while your
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.11,0:32:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,phone is in your pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,different tactic sensations to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.74,0:32:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,inform which way to turn and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.22,0:32:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.54,0:32:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Altogether for perceivability.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.16,0:32:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's legible, audible, and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,tactile.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can use any one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.59,0:32:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,distinctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.99,0:32:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity is something different
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.38,0:32:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,conceptually.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.80,0:32:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We do things for simplicity and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.23,0:32:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to improve perceivability.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.28,0:32:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do things with integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.13,0:32:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The state of being whole and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.68,0:32:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,undivided.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.22,0:32:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When we say someone has
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity with think of them as
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,being honest with an admirable
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.19,0:32:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,moral compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when we consider that the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.07,0:32:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,people who need our services the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.50,0:32:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,most, might be the ones who find
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.55,0:32:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,them the hardest to use, how do
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.85,0:32:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we design with integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.45,0:32:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as designers and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.54,0:32:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,developers, we take
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.32,0:32:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.45,0:33:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When architects build spaces
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.33,0:33:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,today, they make sure they're
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,accessible for everyone because
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.36,0:33:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a human right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.85,0:33:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And when designer draw beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.59,0:33:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,cars, they still have to adhere
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.95,0:33:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to regulations created for human
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.16,0:33:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.18,0:33:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when we design digital
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.57,0:33:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,products, we have to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.72,0:33:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,ourselves accountable for their
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.97,0:33:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.67,0:33:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when we don't we're
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.65,0:33:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding who's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.26,0:33:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year for iOS 10, we
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.33,0:33:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,redesigned Maps from the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.93,0:33:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.62,0:33:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Making it clearer, simpler, easy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.20,0:33:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to use, and faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.22,0:33:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a big undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.53,0:33:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We opened the door on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.54,0:33:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility, but we didn't go
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.22,0:33:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that far along the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.27,0:33:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a busy year.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.69,0:33:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But in iOS 11 we did take
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.23,0:33:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,responsibility, and we made it a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,priority, leveraging the new
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.23,0:33:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,UIKit frameworks and following
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.92,0:33:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the principles that Caroline
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.33,0:33:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,outlined today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.74,0:34:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Making as much text dynamic as
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.35,0:34:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,possible, displaying the same
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.78,0:34:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,amount of text as the default
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.37,0:34:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,UI, using as much of the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.23,0:34:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,width for text.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.70,0:34:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Search is a core component of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.75,0:34:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maps and now it's easier for
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.11,0:34:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not always just as
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.52,0:34:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,simple as increasing the font
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.10,0:34:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,size.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.11,0:34:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you might be thinking, hang
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.22,0:34:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,on, I can see some truncation in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,these screenshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This breaks the principles we're
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.85,0:34:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about, and you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.21,0:34:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes we have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.46,0:34:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,choices based on context.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.20,0:34:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, on the right screen here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.53,0:34:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of the card has a fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.04,0:34:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,header.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.04,0:34:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if we didn't truncate, the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.57,0:34:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,route options beneath would not
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,be scrollable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.67,0:34:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is the card for a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.91,0:34:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're used in different
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.81,0:34:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,context across iOS, including
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.77,0:34:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Spotlight, Safari, and Siri.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.71,0:34:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And from here you start
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.38,0:34:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,navigation, make a call to check
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.11,0:34:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,on your reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.93,0:35:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even have a look at what's
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.99,0:35:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.16,0:35:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Things everyone might like to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.55,0:35:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.14,0:35:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's take a closer look at
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the components of this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.39,0:35:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,design, like the title block.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.58,0:35:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We use this with search results
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.44,0:35:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,too and last year we truncated
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.11,0:35:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the title for long place names
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.57,0:35:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of wrapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.56,0:35:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But with a big of UIKit magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.38,0:35:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,this year, now it does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.55,0:35:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is actually pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.56,0:35:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the component is more
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.39,0:35:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,effective and robust because of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.86,0:35:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.05,0:35:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And we made some changes to the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.13,0:35:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,place card this year to improve
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.52,0:35:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hierarchy including this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.34,0:35:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,secondary row of actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we need to accommodate a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,maximum of five options here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.01,0:35:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.97,0:35:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, on an iPhone 7, in English,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.65,0:35:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.74,0:35:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was such a cheap joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.54,0:36:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,On iPhone 7, in English this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.69,0:36:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,works and we can fit five in a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,row.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we handle it with
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.40,0:36:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic type?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.27,0:36:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we can't just increase
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.44,0:36:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the font size.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.25,0:36:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But we could stack the UI
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.83,0:36:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,elements smartly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.01,0:36:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the way up the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.42,0:36:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Internationalization is a form
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.12,0:36:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of accessibility too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.58,0:36:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And it brings its own
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.37,0:36:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.57,0:36:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how about these labels in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.99,0:36:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.14,0:36:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, they're a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.72,0:36:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if we go back down to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.88,0:36:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,default size, oh, but the label
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.08,0:36:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is truncating.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.87,0:36:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the label is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.76,0:36:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We should try not to truncate it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.45,0:36:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,at any size.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.03,0:36:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But we could apply a similar
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.40,0:36:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,technique like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.96,0:36:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, they remain clear and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.13,0:36:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,uncompromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Adaptive design based on a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.40,0:36:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,user's language and UI settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.19,0:36:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it works better across
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.71,0:36:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,different device sizes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.15,0:37:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And for these actions at the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.26,0:37:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom of the card, as well as
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.17,0:37:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the content, we reflowed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.29,0:37:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the labels and scaled the icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.42,0:37:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Using vector assets, so there's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.21,0:37:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,no pixilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.98,0:37:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we made all the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.33,0:37:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,labels VoiceOver enabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.12,0:37:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And in Maps, we hung out with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.59,0:37:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Siri as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.81,0:37:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there are more complex
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.09,0:37:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,challenges than the ones I just
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.23,0:37:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,illustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.63,0:37:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's easier not to take
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.18,0:37:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.39,0:37:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But challenges are rewarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.78,0:37:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how I ended up;
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.01,0:37:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,challenges are fun and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.92,0:37:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,rewarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I ended up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.46,0:37:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,standing here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.33,0:37:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Designing for everyone is a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.43,0:37:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,process that can bring a deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.34,0:37:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding of your product
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.71,0:37:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.15,0:37:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the few effective keys to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.80,0:37:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the design problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.89,0:37:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The ability of the designer to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.62,0:37:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize as many of the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.89,0:38:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,constraints possible, their
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.42,0:38:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,willingness and enthusiasm for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.34,0:38:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,working within these
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.16,0:38:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.19,0:38:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because out of constraints come
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.50,0:38:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,great solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.86,0:38:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we're designing just for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.98,0:38:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,default settings, we're not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.16,0:38:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,doing it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.19,0:38:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By trying to do better than
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.27,0:38:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that, we make ourselves better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.04,0:38:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we really learned an awful
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.70,0:38:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lot this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.08,0:38:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, secondly after we decide to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.69,0:38:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,take responsibility, we need to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.43,0:38:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,think about empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.36,0:38:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The ability to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.80,0:38:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.12,0:38:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To recognize their wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.12,0:38:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,desires, and feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.78,0:38:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People that are not you --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.29,0:38:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because nobody else is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.34,0:38:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's take a look at a few
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,made-up examples that might be
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.40,0:38:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,closer to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.62,0:38:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.26,0:38:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Never been accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.51,0:38:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something nice to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.31,0:38:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting down with a newspaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.46,0:39:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but not if you can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.74,0:39:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If your vision isn't perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.69,0:39:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,reading one of these has always
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.30,0:39:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,been a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.08,0:39:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of you create
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.12,0:39:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,platforms for content that's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.39,0:39:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,consumed the world over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Platforms with the capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.89,0:39:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to improve the readability of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.30,0:39:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,our content, relatively and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.63,0:39:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.70,0:39:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And platforms, which can be
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.02,0:39:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,navigated and understood through
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.95,0:39:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sound for those who can't read
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.84,0:39:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,visually.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.86,0:39:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we read a lot on our iPhones
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.77,0:39:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or iPads.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.00,0:39:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's good news, other
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.03,0:39:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,times it's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.67,0:39:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, depending on where you look,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be fake news, like
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.95,0:39:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,these revelations about Lorem
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,ipsum.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.93,0:39:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's the same article with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.29,0:39:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,some visual considerations for
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.78,0:39:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic type.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.86,0:39:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The headline is moved outside
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.55,0:39:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the hero image for better
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.18,0:39:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast and for practicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.05,0:40:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the content is readable at
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.74,0:40:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,my preferred size.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.49,0:40:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it still looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.92,0:40:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if you couldn't read a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,price tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What would the experience of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.36,0:40:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,buying things be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.33,0:40:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tap on a price tag to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.68,0:40:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,hear an audio cue, but on an
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.65,0:40:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,iPhone, iPad, or Mac you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.87,0:40:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly that and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.80,0:40:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here we are shopping for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.60,0:40:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,fresh, delicious, emoji-fied
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.18,0:40:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.67,0:40:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a two-column layout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,at default settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.13,0:40:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if we turn up dynamic types
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.48,0:40:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a bit, we could reflow the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.10,0:40:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,content into one linear list.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.97,0:40:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar to how you would on a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,responsive website between
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.98,0:40:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,desktop and mobile breakpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.45,0:40:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving enough space to elements
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.19,0:40:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to make them simpler and easier
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.74,0:40:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.12,0:40:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's our product page for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.26,0:40:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this pineapple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.95,0:40:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Adapting your layout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.93,0:40:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriately makes sure the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.74,0:40:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,most important actions are
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:40:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,available immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.91,0:41:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, again if we bump up the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.98,0:41:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic type that's working
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.15,0:41:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.38,0:41:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, let's turn it up to the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.85,0:41:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.11,0:41:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, but is there more we can
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.34,0:41:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.58,0:41:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we scroll the card, we can
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.00,0:41:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,see the most desired actions are
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.33,0:41:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a little bit far way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.02,0:41:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, maybe we'd consider swapping
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.92,0:41:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,them in this context.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.71,0:41:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And that's definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.89,0:41:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.98,0:41:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what about music,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.12,0:41:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,podcasts, stories, sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.83,0:41:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Audio content is great because
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.26,0:41:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it plays over the air, or your
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.60,0:41:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.69,0:41:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a UI to be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,entertained by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.40,0:41:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do need a UI to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.74,0:41:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to discover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.38,0:41:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the new podcast and music
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.08,0:41:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,apps on iOS 11, the content
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.09,0:41:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,adapts to your preferences and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.69,0:41:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,can be used with VoiceOver, so
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.25,0:41:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone can access it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.40,0:41:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, finally potential energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.55,0:41:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlocking potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.24,0:42:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If we make more things possible
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.32,0:42:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for more types of people, more
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.31,0:42:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,things can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.15,0:42:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome things like iconic
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.18,0:42:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,albums or pioneering science.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.01,0:42:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or miraculous things like
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.57,0:42:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,remembering your friends'
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.74,0:42:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.09,0:42:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple things like sending a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.53,0:42:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,gift or a message to a loved
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.87,0:42:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.72,0:42:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.39,0:42:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're reliant on language and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.62,0:42:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,our remarkable use of it is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.31,0:42:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps the primary reason for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.70,0:42:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,our success as a species.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.95,0:42:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it through colors, text,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.20,0:42:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sound, or signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.30,0:42:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.29,0:42:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,German speakers in the room are
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.59,0:42:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,one step ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.84,0:42:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't communicate in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.89,0:42:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone's language, how can we
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.18,0:42:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,help them accomplish things?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.10,0:42:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Without understanding, we can't
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.34,0:42:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,create any value at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.51,0:42:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I read an amazing article
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.69,0:43:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier this week called, "The
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.84,0:43:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughts of a Spider Web" by
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Joshua Sokol.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.94,0:43:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And in it there was an example
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.06,0:43:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,about how bees use ultraviolet
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.49,0:43:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,vision to find flowers that have
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.81,0:43:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,also evolved ultraviolet
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.41,0:43:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,markings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.19,0:43:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And beside it a quote which
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.46,0:43:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,said, "if you don't have those
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.11,0:43:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,receptors that part of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.74,0:43:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,simply doesn't exist."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.44,0:43:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Design that includes everyone is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.63,0:43:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,not good design, it's great
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.95,0:43:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,design.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.12,0:43:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, design with integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.22,0:43:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Take responsibility, caring
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.06,0:43:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,about everyone's experience, not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.16,0:43:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,just your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.89,0:43:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And be empathetic considering
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.83,0:43:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the perspectives of others who
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.68,0:43:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,interact with the world in
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.91,0:43:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,different ways than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.31,0:43:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And understand that by doing so
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.44,0:43:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we can help unlock potential, in
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.86,0:43:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,tiny and huge ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.52,0:44:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.35,0:44:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, together we can strive
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.78,0:44:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,for simplicity and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.49,0:44:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,perceivability in our apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.30,0:44:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And do it all with integrity for
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.13,0:44:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,making good apps great.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.08,0:44:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I encourage you to start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.14,0:44:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and audit your apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.22,0:44:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Start conversations with your
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.68,0:44:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,team and people who use your
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.45,0:44:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.55,0:44:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And most importantly schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.99,0:44:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,time to see it all the way into
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.68,0:44:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,customers' hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.67,0:44:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly do it proudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.08,0:44:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can give everyone the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.35,0:44:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to be surprised, delighted, feel
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.41,0:44:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,good, and empowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.37,0:44:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We especially as designers would
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.40,0:44:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,always like things to line up
